{"tid":813069,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"FBI緊盯中共延攬計劃　美企「照單炒人」","createTime":"2018-09-10T07:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T01:10:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0c30b970e18105a2276a24b83c5c6c0d65d226ec","tid":813069,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:02:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180910/20496144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180910%2F20496144&d=aYDE9KzYsOpxgFxiHX9xq%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=febef651\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180910%2F20496144&h=ca0c25af\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180910/20496144</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月10日 <br />\n<br />\nFBI緊盯中共延攬計劃　美企「照單炒人」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180910/large/a1805a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180910%2Flarge%2Fa1805a.gif&h=fe062040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地推「千人計劃」吸引華裔學者、科學家。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中美貿易角力升級之際，美國聯邦調查局（FBI）加強對中國科技滲透的防範。除多名美籍華人學者、工程師被以間諜罪名拘查或拒發簽證，FBI還針對中方引進海外人才的「千人計劃」採取行動，照名單嚴查華裔學者，令千人計劃隨時變「入獄計劃」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國華人社交網消息指，休斯頓醫學中心近日來了FBI人員，不知打了甚麼招呼，結果幾位名列中國千人計劃的教授或研究人員被炒。這些人都是行業佼佼者，一旦被解僱還背上間諜嫌疑，在西方難找同樣工作。消息指FBI「照着千人名單調查，一個不漏」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美拘捕多名華裔科學家<br />\n<br />\n此前美方曾以「間諜」罪名拘捕多名華裔科學家，包括美國通用電氣公司（GE）主任工程師鄭小清、美國維珍尼亞理工大學教授張以恆、美國氣象專家王春等；原北京大學生命科學院長饒毅赴美開會被美方拒簽證。這些知名學者都是名列中共千人計劃名單中。<br />\n<br />\n所謂千人計劃，是2008年起由中共中組部牽頭，統戰部、教育部、科技部等發起的招攬海外人才計劃，目標是一千名國外著名大學、科研機構任職的專家學者，國際知名企業專才，擁有自主知識產權或掌握核心技術的人才等。他們獲聘回中國從事全職或短期工作，中方付厚酬。<br />\n<br />\n這項計劃實施十年來一直備受質疑和詬病。美國參議院小組委員會今年6月曾舉行聽證會，題為「千人計劃：中共滲透和利用美國學術界的運動」，披露其背後諜戰疑雲。<br />\n<br />\n推特/美國之音  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n強迫「轉化」　新疆集中營虐待突厥裔人<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n弟買名牌　姐穿舊衫　父母重男輕女　台女大控訴"},{"pid":"c93df64c98d047d5261d549135d5edba3f33bc53","tid":813069,"uid":167658,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:07:55.000Z","msg":"個計劃2008年開始，到侵侵做總統先發覺有問題<br />\nObama真係鳩左8年"},{"pid":"f68073b011d5d128a49be26981762f13d55ecec8","tid":813069,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:16:30.000Z","msg":"炒人名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68bbb412fa4b273bd3685a67e2c5adf1e667488a","tid":813069,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:17:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0b5ade9741be196e908430be0a5e393aea823c","tid":813069,"uid":11148,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:17:40.000Z","msg":"咁撚多間諜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5eaaa7e3ca828a16fa5082e7956b2c04cfdacd0","tid":813069,"uid":90735,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:20:39.000Z","msg":"千人計劃，老千嘅千"},{"pid":"ad6c0604a51e44b52ad7eb2a41d31e1b65933b5d","tid":813069,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a762832eab802597712d0a5b4133acdb676a6cc","tid":813069,"uid":140588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:21:03.000Z","msg":"上次搞在華CIA鬼頭仔，今次美帝復卓！贏國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4f546fe482637632ecff39b873bcbdbf27e3f5","tid":813069,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:25:03.000Z","msg":"啲支國人返工實嚇到標屎，無端端操隊FBI入黎，第二日隔離個華人同事個位就空咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗起matrix<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Lweuy1X9Tcg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLweuy1X9Tcg&d=aYDE9KzYsOpxgFxiHX9xq%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=fcd7f8e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Lweuy1X9Tcg</a>"},{"pid":"84fa0930cb32e2981aacf9b2335cab49516ddf81","tid":813069,"uid":24788,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:26:49.000Z","msg":"富起來10幾年就想做埋大佬<br />\n人地梗係搞9你啦"},{"pid":"0be94d5f5735c4dc7108681c8e7521dbfdfc3535","tid":813069,"uid":182475,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:29:39.000Z","msg":"美國人真係蠢到無藥醫。。。根本出得國有「能力」做研究或成位專科專家果堆 99% 自己都係共產黨員，仲名乜撚嘢單? 最少攞過中國國內獎學金或 funding 果堆就可以即捕即解啦。。。"},{"pid":"892f9e3277a5f7265b492c88048a940dc6ebd4a4","tid":813069,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c93df64c98d047d5261d549135d5edba3f33bc53","tid":813069,"uid":167658,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:07:55.000Z","msg":"個計劃2008年開始，到侵侵做總統先發覺有問題<br />\nObama真係鳩左8年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99abd622b1684d29483cf5516852eca54384c1e7","tid":813069,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b4f546fe482637632ecff39b873bcbdbf27e3f5","tid":813069,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:25:03.000Z","msg":"啲支國人返工實嚇到標屎，無端端操隊FBI入黎，第二日隔離個華人同事個位就空咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗起matrix<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Lweuy1X9Tcg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLweuy1X9Tcg&d=aYDE9KzYsOpxgFxiHX9xq%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=fcd7f8e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Lweuy1X9Tcg</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:33:45.000Z","msg":"美國或將恢復水刑，FBI還有哪些酷刑<br />\n<br />\n1 控頭。審訊人員雙手按着囚犯的面頰，不讓囚犯的頭移動，同時手指不停的指向對方眼睛（要求不能不能觸碰到眼睛）。由於不存在明顯的疼痛，它難以被認為會造成嚴重的身體疼痛或者痛苦。里佐在其書中透露，這一手段曾經使用在祖貝達身上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2 剝奪睡眠。長時間用強光刺激罪犯，致使罪犯無法入睡，人不喝水能存活72小時甚至更長，但是很少有人能72小時不睡覺。<br />\n<br />\n3 壓力姿勢。讓罪犯長時間保持一個使肌肉疲勞的姿勢，比如讓罪犯雙腳向外扭曲坐在地上，雙手高舉過頭頂；或者讓罪犯跪在地上，身體向後傾斜45度。<br />\n<br />\n4 盒子緊閉。把罪犯關在狹小的黑暗空間裏，使其伸展不開身體。有的罪犯被塞進滿足一人站立的盒子，罰站18個小時；有的則需要蜷縮進一個更小的盒子，關上2個小時。囚犯常常被剝光衣服，雙手吊舉過頭。他們還被嘈雜的音樂與噪音轟炸，只有1個水桶充當馬桶，有些罪犯會甚至被強迫穿尿布。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/world/6n8qyjp.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fworld%2F6n8qyjp.html&d=aYDE9KzYsOpxgFxiHX9xq%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=662c747a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/world/6n8qyjp.html</a>"},{"pid":"40725ed6ce6e91653bdf9aa5a099a9341a7d7299","tid":813069,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f68073b011d5d128a49be26981762f13d55ecec8","tid":813069,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:16:30.000Z","msg":"炒人名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:33:54.000Z","msg":"開哂名, 方便FBI做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dfeb5b0b975f416c0d25bbce3cbd1f72f734972","tid":813069,"uid":113000,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:41:13.000Z","msg":"幾時拉埋拎美國護照但日日叫自己中國人個堆叛國人仕"},{"pid":"0b6d90faa76ef8e18a8251c4723cd8c9ea60b681","tid":813069,"uid":66618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a762832eab802597712d0a5b4133acdb676a6cc","tid":813069,"uid":140588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:21:03.000Z","msg":"上次搞在華CIA鬼頭仔，今次美帝復卓！贏國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:43:11.000Z","msg":"捉晒D中國間諜上電椅"},{"pid":"3cb8671c34941430adbe2cd7314a724182782940","tid":813069,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi